local allCM={{label="View NPC (Click)",key="viewNPC"},{label="Kill NPC (Click)",key="killClick"},{label="Fling NPC (Click)",key="fling"},{label="Delete NPC (Click)",key="deleteClick"},{label="Bring NPC (Click)",key="bringClick"},{label="Ragdoll NPC (Click)",key="ragdollClick"}}
local function gAB() local a={}; for k,v in pairs(btns) do a[k]=v end; for k,v in pairs(btns2) do a[k]=v end; return a end
local function dACM(ek) local ab=gAB(); for _,m in ipairs(allCM) do if m.key~=ek and states[m.key] then states[m.key]=false; if ab[m.label] then ab[m.label].Text=m.label end end end end

-- BUTTON LOGIC
track(btns["Kill NPCs (Loop)"].MouseButton1Click:Connect(function() states.killNPCs=not states.killNPCs; btns["Kill NPCs (Loop)"].Text=states.killNPCs and "⏹ Kill: ON" or "Kill NPCs (Loop)"
    if states.killNPCs then task.spawn(function() local ep=loopEpoch; while states.killNPCs and ep==loopEpoch do for _,e in ipairs(allNPCRoots()) do e.hum.Health=0 end; task.wait(0.5) end end) end end))

track(btns["Push NPCs (Loop)"].MouseButton1Click:Connect(function() states.pushNPCs=not states.pushNPCs; btns["Push NPCs (Loop)"].Text=states.pushNPCs and "⏹ Push: ON" or "Push NPCs (Loop)"
    if states.pushNPCs then task.spawn(function() local ep=loopEpoch; while states.pushNPCs and ep==loopEpoch do local mH=player.Character and player.Character:FindFirstChild("HumanoidRootPart")
        if mH then for _,e in ipairs(allNPCRoots()) do if (e.hrp.Position-mH.Position).Magnitude<=pushRange then e.hrp.Velocity=(e.hrp.Position-mH.Position).Unit*pushStrength+Vector3.new(0,20,0) end end end; task.wait(0.1) end end) end end))

track(btns["Fling All NPCs"].MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
    local inR=allNPCRootsInRange(flingRange); local c=0
    for _,e in ipairs(inR) do pcall(function() e.hrp.Velocity=Vector3.new(math.random()*2-1,0.5,math.random()*2-1).Unit*flingStrength; c=c+1 end) end
    btns["Fling All NPCs"].Text="Flung "..c.."!"; task.delay(1.5,function() btns["Fling All NPCs"].Text="Fling All NPCs" end) end))

track(btns["Bring All NPCs"].MouseButton1Click:Connect(function()
    local mH=player.Character and player.Character:FindFirstChild("HumanoidRootPart"); if not mH then return end
    local bn=btns["Bring All NPCs"]; bn.BackgroundColor3=Color3.fromRGB(70,70,70)
    task.spawn(function()
        local npcs=allNPCRoots(); local named=buildDisplayNames(npcs); local fl={}
        for _,item in ipairs(named) do local k=getNPCKey(item.e.model); if next(bringFilter)==nil or bringFilter[k]~=false then table.insert(fl,{e=item.e,display=item.display}) end end
        local tg={}; for i,f in ipairs(fl) do local a=(i/math.max(1,#fl))*math.pi*2; tg[i]=mH.CFrame*CFrame.new(math.cos(a)*4,0,math.sin(a)*4) end
        for att=1,bringAttempts do bn.Text="Lock ("..att.."/"..bringAttempts..")"; local done=true
            for i,f in ipairs(fl) do local ex=pcall(function() local _=f.e.hrp.Position end); if ex and tg[i] and not isNPCAtPos(f.e.hrp,tg[i],2) then done=false; bringNPCToPos(f.e,tg[i],f.display) end end
            if done then break end; if att<bringAttempts then task.wait(0.05) end end
        for i,f in ipairs(fl) do local ex=pcall(function() local _=f.e.hrp.Position end); if ex and tg[i] then bringNPCToPos(f.e,tg[i],f.display) end end
        bn.Text="Bring All NPCs"; bn.BackgroundColor3=Color3.fromRGB(0,135,135) end) end))

track(btns["Delete All NPCs"].MouseButton1Click:Connect(function() for _,e in ipairs(allNPCRoots()) do local k=getNPCKey(e.model); if next(deleteFilter)==nil or deleteFilter[k]~=false then pcall(function() e.model:Destroy() end) end end end))

for _,m in ipairs({{label="View NPC (Click)",key="viewNPC"},{label="Kill NPC (Click)",key="killClick"},{label="Fling NPC (Click)",key="fling"}}) do
    track(btns[m.label].MouseButton1Click:Connect(function() dACM(m.key); states[m.key]=not states[m.key]; btns[m.label].Text=states[m.key] and ("⏹ "..m.label..": ON") or m.label
        if m.key=="viewNPC" and not states.viewNPC and viewingNPC then doUnview() end end)) end
for _,m in ipairs({{label="Delete NPC (Click)",key="deleteClick"},{label="Bring NPC (Click)",key="bringClick"},{label="Ragdoll NPC (Click)",key="ragdollClick"}}) do
    track(btns2[m.label].MouseButton1Click:Connect(function() dACM(m.key); states[m.key]=not states[m.key]; btns2[m.label].Text=states[m.key] and ("⏹ "..m.label..": ON") or m.label end)) end

-- AUTOS
local function setAS(l,k,a) states[k]=a; local b=btns3[l]; if b then b.btn.Text=a and "⏹ ON" or "OFF"; b.dot.BackgroundColor3=a and Color3.fromRGB(0,240,75) or Color3.fromRGB(70,70,70)
    if a then task.spawn(function() while states[k] do TweenService:Create(b.dot,TweenInfo.new(0.4),{BackgroundColor3=Color3.fromRGB(0,240,75)}):Play(); task.wait(0.4)
        if not states[k] then break end; TweenService:Create(b.dot,TweenInfo.new(0.4),{BackgroundColor3=Color3.fromRGB(0,140,35)}):Play(); task.wait(0.4) end
        b.dot.BackgroundColor3=Color3.fromRGB(70,70,70) end) end end end

track(btns3["Auto Fling NPCs"].btn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function() local ns=not states.autoFling; setAS("Auto Fling NPCs","autoFling",ns)
    if ns then task.spawn(function() local ep=loopEpoch; while states.autoFling and ep==loopEpoch do
        for _,e in ipairs(allNPCRootsInRange(flingRange)) do pcall(function() e.hrp.Velocity=Vector3.new(math.random()*2-1,0.5,math.random()*2-1).Unit*flingStrength end) end; task.wait(0.5) end end) end end))

track(btns3["Bring All NPCs (Loop)"].btn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function() local ns=not states.bringLoop; setAS("Bring All NPCs (Loop)","bringLoop",ns)
    if ns then task.spawn(function() local ep=loopEpoch; while states.bringLoop and ep==loopEpoch do local mH=player.Character and player.Character:FindFirstChild("HumanoidRootPart")
        if mH then local npcs=allNPCRoots(); local named=buildDisplayNames(npcs); local fl={}
            for _,item in ipairs(named) do local k=getNPCKey(item.e.model); if next(bringFilter)==nil or bringFilter[k]~=false then table.insert(fl,item) end end
            for i,item in ipairs(fl) do local a=(i/math.max(1,#fl))*math.pi*2; bringNPCToPos(item.e,mH.CFrame*CFrame.new(math.cos(a)*4,0,math.sin(a)*4),item.display) end
        end; task.wait(0.01) end end) end end))

track(btns3["Ragdoll All NPCs (Loop)"].btn.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function() local ns=not states.ragdollLoop; setAS("Ragdoll All NPCs (Loop)","ragdollLoop",ns)
    if ns then task.spawn(function() local ep=loopEpoch; while states.ragdollLoop and ep==loopEpoch do
        for _,e in ipairs(allNPCRoots()) do pcall(function() ragdollNPC(e.model) end) end; task.wait(1) end end) end end))

-- STOP ALL
local function rAU() local ab=gAB(); for _,m in ipairs(allCM) do if ab[m.label] then ab[m.label].Text=m.label end end
    for _,d in ipairs(t1D) do if btns[d.label] then btns[d.label].Text=d.label end end
    for _,b in pairs(btns3) do b.btn.Text="OFF"; b.dot.BackgroundColor3=Color3.fromRGB(70,70,70) end end

track(stB.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function() resetStates(); hideUV(); rAU() end))
track(anB.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function() anchorActive=not anchorActive; anB.Text="Anchor Toggle: "..(anchorActive and "ON" or "OFF"); anB.BackgroundColor3=anchorActive and Color3.fromRGB(0,115,55) or Color3.fromRGB(75,38,38) end))
track(setB.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function() sP.Visible=not sP.Visible end))
track(sPCB.MouseButton1Click:Connect(function() sP.Visible=false end))

-- CLICK HANDLER
track(mouse.Button1Down:Connect(function()
    local t=mouse.Target; if not t then return end
    if anchorActive and t:IsA("BasePart") then t.Anchored=not t.Anchored; return end
    local md=t:FindFirstAncestorOfClass("Model"); if not md then return end
    local hm=md:FindFirstChildOfClass("Humanoid"); local hr=md:FindFirstChild("HumanoidRootPart")
    local isN=hm and not Players:GetPlayerFromCharacter(md); if not isN then return end
    if states.viewNPC then workspace.CurrentCamera.CameraSubject=hm; viewingNPC=true; viewedHumanoid=hm; showUV(); uvB.Text="👁 Unview: "..(md.Name or "NPC")
    elseif states.killClick then hm.Health=0
    elseif states.fling and hr then hr.Velocity=Vector3.new(math.random()*2-1,0.5,math.random()*2-1).Unit*flingStrength
    elseif states.deleteClick then pcall(function() md:Destroy() end)
    elseif states.bringClick then local mH=player.Character and player.Character:FindFirstChild("HumanoidRootPart"); if mH and hr then bringNPCToPos({hum=hm,hrp=hr,model=md},mH.CFrame*CFrame.new(0,0,-5),md.Name) end
    elseif states.ragdollClick then ragdollNPC(md) end
end))

task.spawn(function() while gui.Parent do if viewingNPC and viewedHumanoid then local ok=pcall(function() local _=viewedHumanoid.Health; local _=viewedHumanoid.Parent end)
    if not ok or not viewedHumanoid.Parent or viewedHumanoid.Health<=0 then doUnview() end end; task.wait(0.5) end end)

track(UserInputService.InputBegan:Connect(function(inp,gp)
    if inp.KeyCode==Enum.KeyCode.X and not gp then resetStates(); hideUV(); rAU() end
    if inp.KeyCode==Enum.KeyCode.C then setVis(not gV) end
    if inp.KeyCode==Enum.KeyCode.Insert then setVis(not gV) end
    if inp.KeyCode==Enum.KeyCode.V and viewingNPC then doUnview() end
end))

